DOCKER FILE: TO CREATE IMAGES
DOCKER SWARM: MULTIPLE SERVES SINGLE CONTAINER
DOCKER COMPOSE: MULTIPLE CONTAINER SINGLE SERVER
DOCKER STACK: MULTIPLE CONTAINERS ON MULTIPLE HOSTS


